    "description": {
      "value": "<p>As a move action, you can call upon your deities to grant you courage. You gain a +1 morale bonus on attack rolls, damage rolls, and Will saving throws against fear effects for a number of rounds equal to your Charisma bonus.</p>\n<p>At 7th level, this bonus increases to +2, and at 14th level this bonus increases to +3.</p>\n<p>You can use this ability once per day, plus one additional time per day at 5th level, and every 5 levels thereafter.</p>"
